[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ほらヘルト、見て！　私たちみんなで作ったの！\n美味しそうでしょ……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01335",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "兄者！　我も味見をしたんじゃ！\nすごいじゃろう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01336",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "ヘルト兄様……食欲がないのでしょうか？\nでは私が、食欲増進効果のある柔軟を――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01337",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "ゴゥ兄様、冗談はそこまでにしてください",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01338",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "……正直、想像はしていましたが、今のヘルト兄様の\n心には、私たちの料理でも届かないようですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01339",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "これ、ヘルトは一生このままなんて……ないだろうね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01340",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "なんてこと言うの、シトリン！\nやめてよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01341",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "でも、キューンもそう思ったんじゃない？\n他のみんなも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01342",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "ここまでやっても届かないんだ。\nこれ以上は、僕たちじゃあ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01343",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "それこそ、パルメ族による\n修理が入ったりしない限りは、もう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01344",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "……他に何か、私たちに何かできないでしょうか、\nイェルカ姉上",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01345",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "こればっかりは、アタシにも分かんないな……\n兄弟のこんな様子、初めて見るからね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01346",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ヴァレリアの核が破壊された時とも違う。\nどうすればいいか、皆目見当がつかない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01347",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "案外、時間が解決してくれたりするかも……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01348",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "それはちょっと楽天的なんじゃないのかな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01349",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "……ヘルトはもう一生、このままかもしれない。\nそう覚悟しておいたほうが、現実的でしょ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01350",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "……うっ、うぅ～っ！\nそ、そんなの、っ、やだー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01351",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "キューン……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01352",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "なんで泣くの？　もう二度と、\nヘルトに怒られたりお仕置きされなくて済むのに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01353",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "そ、そうかもしれないけどっ、でもっ、でも～っ！\n",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01354",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "なんだよそれ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01355",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "涙なんぞ流しおって……\n無駄な機能を付けられて、可哀そうな妹よ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01356",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そんな悲しそうなのに、\n涙を流せないあんたのほうが可哀そうよ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01357",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_01358",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……え！？　ヘルト！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01359",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "あ、兄貴……！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01360",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "なぜ、急に……！？　向こうには調理器具があり、\n今のヘルト兄様には危険です",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01361",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私、見てくる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01362",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]